<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/>
    <title lang="en">Etherpad</title>
    <link type="text/css" href="./static/plugins/ep_user_pads/static/css/styles.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
</head>
<body>
<div id="wrapper">
    <header>
        <div class="inside">
            <nav id="mainMenu">
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="home.html" lang="en">Home</a></li>
                    <li class="separator">|</li>
                    <li><a href="pads.html" lang="en">Public Pads</a></li>
                    <li class="separator">|</li>
                    <li><a href="groups.html" lang="en">My Groups</a></li>
                    <li class="separator">|</li>
                    <li><a class="active" lang="en">Help</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
            <nav id="sekMenu">
                <ul>
                    <li><a lang="en" id="userProfile"><%= username %></a></li>
                    <li class="separator">|</li>
                    <li><a href="#" lang="en" id="logout">Logout</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
            <img src="./static/plugins/ep_user_pads/static/images/logo_tug_grey_white-01.png" alt="Etherpad"
                 id="logo">
        </div>
    </header>
    <div id="main">
        <div class="inside">
            <div class="leftArea">
                <div class="inputBlock">
                    <div class="headline">
                        <h1 lang="en">How to create a private pad?</h1>
                    </div>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Open &quot;<a href="groups.html">My Groups</a>&quot;</li>
                        <li>Under &quot;Create Private Group&quot; enter a groupname (this name must not exist on the
                            sytem yet) and click on the button &quot;Create&quot;. The new group should be listed under
                            &quot;Open Private Groups&quot; now.
                        </li>
                        <li>If you want to add/invite users, click on the users symbol
                            <img src="./static/plugins/ep_user_pads/static/images/users-gold-16.png"/>
                        </li>
                        <li>Click on the group name to switch to the group page.</li>
                        <li>Now enter a pad name under &quot;Create Private Group Pad&quot; and click on on the button
                            &quot;Create&quot;. The new pad should be listed under &quot;Manage Private Group Pads&quot;
                            now.
                        </li>
                        <li>Click on the pad name to switch to the pad page.</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rightArea">
                &nbsp;
            </div>
            <div style="clear: both"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <div class="inside">
            <p lang="en"><a href="./imprint.html">Imprint</a></p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</div>

<script src="./static/plugins/ep_user_pads/static/js/client/jquery.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
<script src="./static/plugins/ep_user_pads/static/js/client/retina.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
<script src="./static/plugins/ep_user_pads/static/js/client/etherpad.js" type="text/javascript"></script>

</body>
</html>
